- Wait, I'll do it myself.

01:21:45.874 --> 01:21:47.374
Go.

01:21:50.541 --> 01:21:52.124
Well done, that's it.

01:21:52.249 --> 01:21:57.791
When they've got their backs to you,
you come out, got it?

