You come out...

01:21:59.416 --> 01:22:00.999
Shut up!

01:22:01.124 --> 01:22:03.624
- You come out, got it?
- Why are you locking it?

01:22:03.749 --> 01:22:06.499
Don't worry, take it easy.

01:22:06.624 --> 01:22:10.041
