- I'll take this off, too.

01:22:11.666 --> 01:22:13.332
Stand by, Simone.

01:22:14.332 --> 01:22:16.207
I don't get why you looked it.

01:22:17.374 --> 01:22:22.082
They're coming.
Hear that? Look, they're coming.

01:22:23.416 --> 01:22:24.957
