01:22:57.666 --> 01:22:59.666
- Holy mother!
- Open it!

01:23:03.416 --> 01:23:04.707
Open it, Marcello.

01:23:05.416 --> 01:23:07.624
- I'm gonna kill you. Open it!
- Mamma mia.

01:23:07.749 --> 01:23:09.082
Open it!

01:23:09.957 --> 01:23:11.166
Well?

01:23:12.916 --> 01:23:14.416
